author: Reuters Editorial
description: India has reported cases of the Zika virus, the World Health Organization said, adding that efforts should be made to strengthen surveillance.
title: WHO says India reports cases of Zika virus

description: NEW DELHI: The Health Ministry on Saturday said there was no cause for worry after the World Health Organisation (WHO) confirmed three cases of mosquito-borne Zika virus in the country.
title: WHO confirms 3 Zika cases in India, health ministry says no cause for worry - Times of India
